123
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:47,390
There's only one in the world.

124
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,370
I made it myself.

125
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,770
Don't lose it.

126
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:10,650
Alright.

127
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:14,480
