140
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,590
Li Jin Bu.

141
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:22,570
I'll wait for you.

142
00:11:29,950 --> 00:11:31,420
Li Jin Bu.

143
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,390
I'll wait for you.

144
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,820
