187
00:14:35,790 --> 00:14:37,350
Because I like her.

188
00:14:38,230 --> 00:14:39,870
If that's what she wants.

189
00:14:44,070 --> 00:14:44,860
Alright.

190
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:46,970
