214
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:30,910
[At the hotel?]

215
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,190
[Why didn't you go out?]

216
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,460
Oh please.

217
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:36,960
As soon as we arrived,

218
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:38,930
