219
00:16:38,930 --> 00:16:40,450
Talking about something urgent.

220
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,920
[I'm new here,]

221
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,650
[so I have no place to go.]

222
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:46,500
Too bad.

223
00:16:48,090 --> 00:16:49,110
[What about you?]

224
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:51,490
[Why are you staying in the dorm?]

225
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:53,770
[You've graduated.]

226
00:16:53,770 --> 00:16:55,950
