a romantic time with Duan Xiao?]

227
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:01,910
[Hello?]

228
00:17:03,850 --> 00:17:04,470
[Hello?]

229
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,710
[Hua, why aren't you talking?]

230
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,280
Li Qing Tong

231
00:17:13,290 --> 00:17:14,800
When will you be back?

232
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,480
What's going on?

233
00:17:17,710 --> 00:17:18,720
I just miss you so much.

234
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:24,250
Hua, are you crying?

235
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,560
No.

236
00:17:26,869 --> 00:17:27,359
[This can't be right.]

237
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,540
[There must be something
going on with you.]

238
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:30,270
What's wrong? Don't make me worry.

239
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:31,100
[I'm fine.]

240
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:32,740
Have a good time.

241
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:33,950
I'll wait for you to come back.

242
00:17:33,950 --> 00:17:35,140
I'll hang up.

243
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:00,430
[Hello.]

244
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,360
Hello.

245
00:19:01,610 --> 00:19:02,860
It's Qing Tong.

246
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:04,550
Are you with Hua now?

247
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:05,590
[No. I am outside.]

248
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,940
[I'm going to attend an interview.]

249
00:19:08,450 --> 00:19:10,420
Is there something going on with Hua
recently?

250
00:19:11,010 --> 00:19:11,770
