gotten into her lately.]

253
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:17,030
[She looks very depressed.]

254
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,460
[Do you remember that last time?]

255
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:19,920
[This is even worse.]

256
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:21,220
[We don't know what happened.]

257
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:22,690
[She's not talking.]

258
00:19:28,150 --> 00:19:28,950
I got it.

259
00:19:29,370 --> 00:19:30,850
You two take care of her.

260
00:19:30,850 --> 00:19:31,930
I'll be back soon.

261
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:33,020
