281
00:20:19,610 --> 00:20:21,110
I can do it, so can you.

282
00:20:27,420 --> 00:20:28,250
Let's go.

283
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:29,100
One more game.

284
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:31,440
Okay.

285
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:32,320
Let's go.

286
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:29,950
