296
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,580
I'll cheer you up.

297
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:10,010
But now, looking at you,

298
00:22:10,860 --> 00:22:12,240
I don't know what to do.

299
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,060
How do I look?

300
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:17,610
Like you lost your soul.

301
00:22:25,010 --> 00:22:26,520
Where is

302
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,580
Li Qing Tong?

303
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:32,410
She went to Beijing with Wu Zhi Xun.

304
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,540
You still like her?

305
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:47,850
Yes.

306
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:50,130
I admit that I still like her.

307
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:54,030
But, I don't think

308
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:58,410
I'll ever get the chance.

309
00:23:00,410 --> 00:23:02,510
But no matter what happens to her,

310
00:23:02,510 --> 00:23:03,320
I will be there for her.

311
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,570
I will help her.

312
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,100
Other than that,

313
00:23:08,770 --> 00:23:09,620
I don't care.

314
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:14,610
I was used to being alone

315
00:23:14,610 --> 00:23:16,450
and I never care for others.

316
00:23:18,730 --> 00:23:19,810
So in the future,

317
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:23,300
I'd better do something consensual.

318
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:31,660
I'm sorry.

319
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:34,690
For what?

320
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:37,160
I used to think you're a jerk.

321
00:23:38,170 --> 00:23:39,650
But now I think I was wrong.

322
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:42,500
Enjoy your meal.

323
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:19,620
Qing Tong.

324
00:24:23,490 --> 00:24:24,700
You're back.

325
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:27,650
I know it's late now.

326
00:24:28,490 --> 00:24:29,960
But I really can't leave earlier.

327
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:32,270
I skipped midnight snack

328
00:24:32,900 --> 00:24:34,670
to come back to you.

329
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:36,710
It's okay.

330
00:24:37,220 --> 00:24:38,100
It's just today.

331
00:24:38,100 --> 00:24:39,360
We'll go out tomorrow.

332
00:24:41,810 --> 00:24:42,760
Tomorrow

333
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:45,030
I need to go there too.

334
00:24:49,990 --> 00:24:51,880
So why did you want me here?

335
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:56,410
Experience the hotel of big city?

336
00:24:56,410 --> 00:24:57,250
It's not like that.

337
00:24:57,250 --> 00:24:58,470
Hear me out.

338
00:24:58,930 --> 00:25:01,910
Professor He's assistant got sick.

339
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:04,700
And this is a great opportunity for me.

340
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:07,960
He's been introducing me around.

341
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:10,740
So it'll be really rude

342
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:12,460
if I don't show up tomorrow.

343
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:14,190
I'm so sorry.

344
00:25:16,190 --> 00:25:16,830
Alright.

345
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,290
Go do your things.

346
00:25:18,290 --> 00:25:19,180
Leave me alone.

347
00:25:20,900 --> 00:25:21,700
Qing Tong.

348
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:25,150
We'll get plenty of time for fun.

349
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:26,490
But now,

350
00:25:26,910 --> 00:25:29,380
we need to think for our future.

351
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,940
I don't want to end up like my parents,

352
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:34,550
leaving all hopes
with the next generation.

353
00:25:34,550 --> 00:25:35,860
I understand.

354
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:38,960
But it was you who wanted me here.

355
00:25:39,290 --> 00:25:42,150
I didn't want to be here
to interfere with your work.

356
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:44,920
I already said I'm sorry.

357
00:25:45,730 --> 00:25:47,160
I know it's my fault.

358
00:25:48,170 --> 00:25:49,750
But plan changes.

359
00:25:50,170 --> 00:25:51,850
And here we are.

360
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:54,160
I can't let such a good chance slip

361
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,720
through my fingers for accompanying you.

362
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,030
Right.

363
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:05,580
You lose this chance because of me.

364
00:26:05,580 --> 00:26:06,560
It's my fault.

365
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:09,360
I don't mean to ignore you,

366
00:26:10,630 --> 00:26:12,150
but people like us from nowhere

367
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,670
need to grab every opportunity.

368
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:18,110
I don't have their good family
or experience.

369
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:20,630
So I have to work harder.

370
00:26:20,630 --> 00:26:22,220
Much harder than them. You know?

371
00:26:22,220 --> 00:26:24,370
Yes, I know.

372
00:26:24,860 --> 00:26:26,680
You don't have to tell me.

373
00:26:27,380 --> 00:26:29,820
What exactly did I do to make you so torn?

374
00:26:30,450 --> 00:26:33,520
I've already done everything you said.

375
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,950
Can't I even complain?

376
00:26:37,290 --> 00:26:38,930
I didn't mean that.

377
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:41,330
I'm talking sense to you.

378
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:43,550
Stop that.

379
00:26:43,970 --> 00:26:46,380
I don't know how to
get along with you now.

380
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,810
You are always

381
00:26:49,810 --> 00:26:51,570
the reasonable and rational one.

382
00:26:54,810 --> 00:26:55,560
I don't want to talk to you.

383
00:26:56,370 --> 00:26:57,080
Qing Tong.

384
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:02,830
Calm down, please.

385
00:27:03,710 --> 00:27:06,020
We finally get several days
to stay together.

386
00:27:06,490 --> 00:27:07,660
So no quarrelling, okay?

387
00:27:08,630 --> 00:27:09,510
Please don't be angry.

388
00:27:10,050 --> 00:27:11,150
I'm sorry.

389
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,360
Trust me.

390
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:49,750
I will come back earlier today.

391
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:52,940
Hurry up.

392
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:53,910
Don't be late.

393
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:54,790
Wait for me.

394
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:00,280
Bye.

395
00:28:09,730 --> 00:28:10,330
It's pretty good.

396
00:28:11,250 --> 00:28:13,730
Good work for

397
00:28:13,730 --> 00:28:14,650
you two newcomers.

398
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,390
It's all because of you, Mr Luo.

399
00:28:17,390 --> 00:28:18,140
Alright.

400
00:28:18,690 --> 00:28:21,130
You don't have to give out flyers anymore.

401
00:28:21,130 --> 00:28:23,220
Come do research with me.

402
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:25,230
Thank you, Mr Luo.

403
00:28:25,230 --> 00:28:26,240
Goodbye, Mr Luo.

404
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:46,380
[Something must have happened to Hua.
I have to go check on her.]

405
00:28:46,410 --> 00:28:47,630
[Focus on your work.
I will visit you next time.]

406
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:49,050
You see,

407
00:28:49,050 --> 00:28:50,940
my dad has talked to Mr Luo.

408
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:53,040
As soon as the head office approves,

409
00:28:53,670 --> 00:28:55,440
we'll start our own business.

410
00:28:56,020 --> 00:28:57,960
Starting the business
right after graduation.

411
00:28:58,450 --> 00:28:59,850
What a promising future.

412
00:28:59,850 --> 00:29:01,520
Right, buddy?

413
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:03,410
Great.

414
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:06,600
Thank you Mr Jiang.

415
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:07,730
That's alright. That's alright.

416
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:10,180
So,

417
00:29:10,590 --> 00:29:12,280
where will we go

418
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,250
for our research?

419
00:29:13,250 --> 00:29:14,250
To the south.

420
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:16,050
The south is full of opportunities.

421
00:29:17,390 --> 00:29:18,330
Well,

422
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,830
how long will we stay?

423
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:23,410
I'm not sure.

424
00:29:24,410 --> 00:29:26,170
Maybe a lifetime.

425
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:29,750
What?

426
00:29:32,890 --> 00:29:33,620
In that case,

427
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,680
I need to think about it.

428
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:39,490
Why? It's such a good chance!

429
00:29:40,580 --> 00:29:42,860
It's about her?

430
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:43,990
Please.

431
00:29:44,870 --> 00:29:45,660
It's not about her.

432
00:29:47,390 --> 00:29:48,310
Dude,

433
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:51,130
there're plenty of fish in the sea.

434
00:29:51,130 --> 00:29:52,640
You'll find your Miss Right.

435
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:55,240
I'll set you up with other girls.

436
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,510
Just worry about yourself.

437
00:29:58,760 --> 00:29:59,940
You don't believe me?

438
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:02,170
The girls I introduce to you
are much better than Li Qing Tong.

439
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:17,840
What wish did you make?

440
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:21,860
I wish that I can
get your present every year.

441
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:23,340
Of course you will.

442
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:22,130
Qing Tong.

443
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:24,150
I brought you something to eat.

444
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,170
Qing Tong

445
00:31:50,410 --> 00:31:51,450
I'm back.

446
00:31:56,570 --> 00:31:58,510
Where are they?

447
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:07,150
Hello.

448
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:11,650
Okay.

449
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,060
How's your trip to Beijing?

450
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:30,310
Not too bad.

451
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:32,110
Just way too many people

452
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:32,900
and cars.

453
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:36,940
What's up?

454
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,260
I was just wondering

455
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:41,440
if you have seen Hua?

456
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,690
Is there anything going on with her?

457
00:32:42,690 --> 00:32:44,160
Why she doesn't answer my call?

458
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:46,520
You haven't heard about it yet?

459
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:49,070
What?

460
00:33:08,010 --> 00:33:10,320
Come on, you don't have to
follow me everywhere.

461
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:11,040
Yes, we do.

462
00:33:11,510 --> 00:33:12,970
If anything happens to you,

463
00:33:12,970 --> 00:33:14,390
Li Qing Tong will kill us both.

464
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:16,420
Nothing will happen to me.

465
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:17,300
Li Jin Bu!

466
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,560
When did you come back?

467
00:33:19,770 --> 00:33:20,690
I just got back.

468
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:22,630
Why didn't you answer my call?

469
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:25,910
You go to Beijing for fun without me,

470
00:33:26,250 --> 00:33:27,500
so I don't want to talk to you.

471
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:44,480
You two go back.

472
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,610
I need to talk to her alone.

473
00:33:46,100 --> 00:33:46,730
Okay.

474
00:33:52,570 --> 00:33:53,970
I don't understand.

475
00:33:53,970 --> 00:33:54,970
You two are a right match.

476
00:33:54,970 --> 00:33:56,730
Why break up?

477
00:33:59,810 --> 00:34:00,850
Don't ask me anything.

478
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:03,030
I finally let it go.

479
00:34:03,790 --> 00:34:05,760
Why do you have to remind me of it?

480
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:07,700
I just don't think

481
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:10,889
you two ought to break up.

482
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:15,760
There's no ‘ought to’ in a relationship.

483
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:18,190
Only ‘willing to'.

484
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:34,659
I just...

485
00:34:35,070 --> 00:34:37,100
I just don't want to be with him.

486
00:34:49,830 --> 00:34:51,170
You expect me to buy that?

487
00:34:58,230 --> 00:34:59,440
Just stop asking me.

488
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:01,660
If you ever mention it again,

489
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:03,890
I'll keep starving myself

490
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:05,790
until I'm dead.

491
00:35:06,200 --> 00:35:08,560
And you'll be sorry for my death.

492
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:25,850
[Is Li Jin Bu alright?]

493
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:29,840
She's okay.

494
00:35:31,570 --> 00:35:32,910
[Are you still mad at me?]

495
00:35:35,340 --> 00:35:36,100
Of course not.

496
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:39,840
[Then why didn't you tell me in advance?]

497
00:35:40,810 --> 00:35:42,480
[You just left me a note.]

498
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,250
[It got me so worried.]

499
00:35:46,010 --> 00:35:47,200
I'm a grown-up

500
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,290
and it's not my first time
to go on a long journey.

501
00:35:48,290 --> 00:35:49,800
There's nothing to worry about.

502
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:52,180
I just didn't want you to

503
00:35:52,660 --> 00:35:55,500
think too much,

504
00:35:55,500 --> 00:35:58,650
or go to such an important
meeting in a mood.

505
00:35:59,630 --> 00:36:00,750
[So promise me.]

506
00:36:01,170 --> 00:36:03,190
[You'll never leave
without saying goodbye.]

507
00:36:04,580 --> 00:36:05,250
I promise.

508
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:08,740
[There's another thing
I need to tell you.]

509
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:10,120
Hua is back.

510
00:36:10,120 --> 00:36:11,180
I have to hang up.

511
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:28,650
[Congratulations, Zhi Xun.]

512
00:36:28,780 --> 00:36:30,990
[You will most definitely get the place.]

513
00:36:31,540 --> 00:36:33,190
[And I've talked to your father.]

514
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,650
[You need to work hard.]

515
00:36:34,820 --> 00:36:36,710
[Don't let us down.]

516
00:36:54,060 --> 00:36:55,560
I come back

517
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:58,330
to talk to you about studying abroad.

518
00:36:58,330 --> 00:36:59,560
Your mother and I

519
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:01,480
will give you our full support.

520
00:37:02,120 --> 00:37:03,760
Actually, I want to stay at home.

521
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,800
Son,

522
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,360
this is our determination.

523
00:37:07,870 --> 00:37:08,800
What's this?

524
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,480
Studying abroad will cost plenty of money.

525
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:13,340
So we sold the house

526
00:37:13,340 --> 00:37:15,770
for you to study abroad.

527
00:37:16,350 --> 00:37:18,170
Our savings are also here.

528
00:37:18,170 --> 00:37:19,260
If you need more,

529
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:20,940
I'll figure it out.

530
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:21,730
No way.

531
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:23,330
You give me all your savings
and the house has been sold.

532
00:37:23,330 --> 00:37:24,340
How are you going to live?

533
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:25,430
It's not something you should worry about.

534
00:37:25,980 --> 00:37:26,990
But it makes me feel like...

535
00:37:26,990 --> 00:37:27,690
Son,

536
00:37:28,700 --> 00:37:30,300
you're an ambitious boy.

537
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,910
All that your mom and I ever wanted

538
00:37:32,910 --> 00:37:35,170
is to raise a boy like you.

539
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,440
Now you have the opportunity.

540
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,690
Your mother and I don't need anything,

541
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:40,250
as long as you can achieve success.

542
00:37:40,930 --> 00:37:42,010
And we'll be happy.

543
00:37:44,620 --> 00:37:46,250
I know I'm not a good father.

544
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:47,990
I've been pushing you very hard

545
00:37:47,990 --> 00:37:49,290
ever since you were a little boy.

546
00:37:49,910 --> 00:37:51,000
I know you hate me.

547
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:52,680
I hate myself too.

548
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:54,500
But, I really

549
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,510
really want you to become
an important person

550
00:37:58,180 --> 00:38:00,030
and go out to broaden your horizon.

551
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,180
Don't end up like me,

552
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,280
mediocre and unambitious,

553
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,780
living in a dreamworld.

554
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,040
Why are you here?

555
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:24,860
I need to talk to you.

556
00:38:26,870 --> 00:38:28,810
Just give me a call.

557
00:38:28,810 --> 00:38:29,980
Why bother coming all the way here?

558
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,500
I think

559
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:34,860
I need to tell you about this

560
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,200
in person.

561
00:38:40,570 --> 00:38:41,910
What?

562
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:44,890
Have you eaten?

563
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:47,240
Let's find some place
to talk while eating.

564
00:38:49,210 --> 00:38:49,970
Okay.

565
00:38:54,010 --> 00:38:54,710
Thanks.

566
00:38:55,020 --> 00:38:55,720
Wait.

567
00:38:58,370 --> 00:38:59,720
I thought you have something to tell me.

568
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:00,340
Go ahead.

569
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:04,710
It's not something important.

570
00:39:05,170 --> 00:39:06,470
Well,

571
00:39:06,470 --> 00:39:08,700
I got the exchange student placement.

572
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:09,580
Really?

573
00:39:11,130 --> 00:39:12,700
That's so great.

574
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:15,170
I thought you didn't get in.

575
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:17,690
So,

576
00:39:17,690 --> 00:39:18,870
how long are you gonna stay there?

577
00:39:20,250 --> 00:39:21,590
I checked before.

578
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,490
Exchange students

579
00:39:23,490 --> 00:39:25,080
generally will study abroad for one year.

580
00:39:27,090 --> 00:39:28,190
What?

581
00:39:29,460 --> 00:39:30,580
Yes, it's one year

582
00:39:30,580 --> 00:39:31,880
for exchange students.

583
00:39:32,680 --> 00:39:33,610
But,

584
00:39:33,610 --> 00:39:35,590
I plan to stay longer.

585
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:37,510
We've agreed that

586
