608
00:40:44,620 --> 00:40:45,720
So how about me?

609
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:50,130
I mean nothing to you?

610
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:52,020
That's why

611
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,500
I want to talk to you face to face.

612
00:40:55,210 --> 00:40:57,430
